headline: Baker Hughes, NextDecade Enter Framework Agreement for Rio Grande LNG Expansion Trains
summary: HOUSTON, March 11, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Baker Hughes (NASDAQ: BKR), an energy technology company, and NextDecade Corporation (NASDAQ: NEXT) and announced Tuesday that they have entered into a framework agreement whereby NextDecade plans to utilize Baker Hughes’ gas turbine and refrigerant compressor technology (Equipment Packages) and enter into contractual services agreements to perform maintenance work for these Equipment Packages for Trains 4 through 8 at the Rio Grande LNG Facility. “Uti
